{!</table>!}

@coalition_menu

- @labour_majority_option: Form a Labour Government.
- @liberals_majority_option: Form a Liberal Government.
- @conservative_majority_option: Realize a Tory Victory.
- @no_majority: Proceed with a Hung Parliament.

@conservative_majority_option
title: It appears the Conservatives have won or lead.
subtitle: Tories hold a majority of the seats.
choose-if: conservative_majority == 1
unavailable-subtitle: The Conservatives won a majority of seats.

The Tories have won a Majority!

- @conservative_majority_sure: Hand over the keys to the government.

@conservative_majority_sure
