@liberal_vonc
title: Liberal Withdrawal of Confidence
new-page: true
tags: event
priority: -1
view-if: in_labour_minority == 1 and liberal_dissent >= 100
on-arrival: in_labour_minority = 0; labour_in_government = 0;
on-departure: next_election_year = year; next_election_month = month; in_election = 1;

The Liberals have withdrawn their confidence and carried a motion of no confidence in the government. Parliament is dissolved and fresh elections are called.

The Liberals have withdrawn their confidence and carried a motion of no confidence in the government. Parliament is dissolved and fresh elections are called.
